	(95, 1, '2025-04-17 08:59:47', '2025-04-17 07:59:47', '<span class="introduction-paragraph">A lovely bright newly extensively renovated seaside house, with sea views, 200m from the beach, and Worthing town centre.</span>\n\nA perfect house in a perfect location, the award winning crab shack restaurant is at the end of the street and the terrace over looks Coast Cafe, The volley ball sand courts, Play park and Splash point. 2 mins walk along the seafront to the Pier, and The Dome.\n\nSleeps 12, 1 min to the beach with with sea views:\n\nThe rooms are large and have been completely renovated, giving the house an elegant stylish feel but it still retains its quirky character.\n\nThe dining table will sit up to 10 people and the kitchen has everything youll need to cook a proper meal, basic ingredients (tea, coffee, etc.) are provided.\n\nThe bedrooms are configured as, 2x King bedrooms one ensuite a double and a twin, and a single daybed for an extra guest.\nThe house has 2 bathrooms.\n\nParking is on street with permits we provide for free. We can provide parking permits for a maximum of 3 cars. Theres a good WIFI connection, a new smart TV that you can access your Netflix account.', 'York House. A bright newly renovated seaside house, with sea views', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'york-house-a-bright-newly-renovated-seaside-house-with-sea-views', '', '', '2025-04-21 10:12:06', '2025-04-21 09:12:06', '', 0, 'http://worthingaccomodationv2/?post_type=properties&#038;p=95', 1, 'properties', '', 0),
