	(113, 1, '2025-04-17 09:03:24', '2025-04-17 08:03:24', '<strong data-end="132" data-start="79">Charming Two-Floor Studio Apartment on a beach Road</strong>\n\nThis cosy and well-appointed one-bedroom studio apartment is perfect for those looking for a comfortable and convenient living space. Located on a desirable Beach Road, it offers easy access to the beach and nearby attractions.\n\nThe studio features a spacious open-plan living area with a comfortable sofa, ideal for relaxing or entertaining guests. The drink preparation area, along with a handy hotplate, makes it easy to prepare meals for yourself.\n\nUpstairs, youll find two single beds, providing a restful space for sleep. while the bathroom offers modern fixtures. In addition, there is a separate toilet for added convenience.\n\nFor your comfort, the apartment comes with flat screen TV, and high-speed WiFi is included, making it perfect for both short stays and longer-term living', 'The Motor House - Charming Two-Floor Studio Apartment - Sleeps 2', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'the-motor-house-charming-two-floor-studio-apartment-sleeps-2', '', '', '2025-04-18 15:11:19', '2025-04-18 14:11:19', '', 0, 'http://worthingaccomodationv2/?post_type=properties&#038;p=113', 3, 'properties', '', 0),
