	(116, 1, '2025-04-17 09:04:19', '2025-04-17 08:04:19', 'Waves, a property with a terrace, is situated in West Worthing, 35 km from Goodwood House, 47 km from Chichester Harbour, as well as 17 km from Arundel Castle.\n\nBoth free WiFi and parking on-site are accessible at the apartment free of charge. The property is non-smoking and is set 300 metres from Worthing Beach.\n\nThe spacious apartment has 2 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, bed linen, towels, a flat-screen TV with streaming services, a dining area, a fully equipped kitchen, and a balcony with sea views. Guests can take in the ambience of the surroundings from an outdoor dining area or keep themselves warm by the fireplace on colder days. For added privacy, the accommodation features a private entrance.\n\nAmberley Castle is 23 km from Waves, while Devils Dyke is 24 km away. The nearest airport is London Gatwick Airport, 51 km from the accommodation.', 'Waves - Two bedroom apartment with sea views - Sleeps 6', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'waves-two-bedroom-apartment-with-sea-views-sleeps-6', '', '', '2025-04-18 15:11:08', '2025-04-18 14:11:08', '', 0, 'http://worthingaccomodationv2/?post_type=properties&#038;p=116', 2, 'properties', '', 0),
